Install Pillow before running the script:

pip install pillow

▶️ How to Use

Place all input images inside the images/ folder

Open and edit the script variables:

input_folder = "images"
output_folder = "output"
new_size = (800, 800)  # width x height
output_format = "JPEG"  # PNG, JPEG, WEBP, etc.


Run the script:

python resize.py
4.All resized images will be saved in output/
